item.title: Week 2019 01
item.description: Yes it's true. I've started a blog again. Besides random howtos that I come across, every week I would like to add a journal entry, spent on anything that I've found interesting during the last week. If you don't have anything better to do (I hope you have), feel free to continue reading. Blogging Technology First of all, on the technology I've used for the blog itself.
